  <!-- Introducción de la actividad -->  
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="narrative-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this Number Talk is to elicit strategies and understandings students have for dividing by 8. These understandings help students develop fluency and will be helpful later in this lesson when students will need to be able to divide when solving problems.</p>
<p>When students use multiplication facts they know to divide and then add or remove groups of 8 for facts they are less familiar with, they look for and make use of structure (MP7).</p>
  </paragraphs>

  <!-- Materiales requeridos de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="materials-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[mmmmmmmmmm]</p>
    <!-- <xi:include href="./warm-converNum-dividamosEntre8-mat.ptx"/>  -->
  </paragraphs>

  <!-- Launch -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="launch-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Display one expression.</li>
      <li>
        <q>Hagan una señal cuando tengan una respuesta y puedan explicar cómo la obtuvieron</q>
      </li>
      <li>1 minute: quiet think time</li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>

  <!-- Instrucciones para el desarrollo de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="instructions-teacher-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Record answers and strategy.</li>
      <li>Keep expressions and work displayed.</li>
      <li>Repeat with each expression.</li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>

